METATRON CUBE (c) NEO.ca

Release Date: 09/2018 Protection: Discs: 1 Genre: Action

METATRON CUBE DEMO AVAILABLE ON OUR SITE Sci-fi action adventure
shooter video game. Futuristic design 3d environment & FPS You take
part in a space expedition whose mission is to explore and
investigate a mysterious space installation... Overcome the
obstacles, enemies and find out what it is and what is it purpose
FPS (First Person Shooter) - Many different levels with original
futuristic 3d environments - Many different enemies like (animals
creatures, monsters, aliens, zombies, soldiers, robots) - A wide
range of futuristic weapons and vehicles - Funny and unexpected
audio speeches from in-game characters

For more info go to: http://store.steampowered.com/app/740340/

1. Extract release
2. Mount ISO
3. Install the game
4. Play!

General Notes:

Block the game's exe in your firewall to prevent the game from
trying to go online
If you install games to your systemdrive, it may be necessary
to run this game with admin privileges instead
